279
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:07,950
Su...

280
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:35,440
10,000 METERS BELOW SEA LEVEL "THE DEEP"
(THE BOTTOM OF THE OCEANIC TRENCH)

281
00:19:43,910 --> 00:19:46,490
I... I'm alive!

282
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:54,460
Light? This deep in the sea?

283
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:57,420
It's too bright! My eyes are dazzled!

284
00:19:57,420 --> 00:20:00,550
But I don't have eyes to be dazzled.

285
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:04,390
Hey guys, come here!

286
00:20:04,390 --> 00:20:06,720
Look at that!

287
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,680
I can't see it--it's too bright.

288
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,390
Hey Nami, is that it?

289
00:20:11,390 --> 00:20:16,270
Yeah, there's no doubt.
The needle is pointing at the island!

290
00:20:16,270 --> 00:20:17,400
That is...

291
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:21,240
The Fish-Man Island!

292
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,290
It's huge!

293
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:39,550
It's in a big bubble! There are
clouds? Maybe there is air inside.

294
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:44,010
That's the Fish-Man Island
so we're 10,000 meters deep now!

295
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:49,180
How is there such a big
tree this deep in the water?

296
00:20:59,730 --> 00:21:03,150
Yeah! We made it!

297
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:06,820
It's a popular site in the Grand Line!

298
00:21:08,490 --> 00:21:10,620
They made it there!

299
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:17,330
The Mermaids dance around
here. The beautiful Mermaids!

300
00:21:17,330 --> 00:21:19,710
I'm finally here!

301
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:23,010
The paradise that I've been
dreaming of since I was a kid!

302
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:30,850
