Mermai...

304
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:36,190
Sanji! You're not ready!
You shouldn't even think about it!

305
00:21:36,190 --> 00:21:37,060
Sanji!

306
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:50,450
I'm sorry, Sanji! The rehab didn't work yet!

307
